*asterisk-1.8.15.0 (31 Jul 2012)

  31 Jul 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +asterisk-1.8.15.0.ebuild:
  Bugfix release on the 1.8 branch. Fixes, among other things, a null pointer
  dereference in ast_sockaddr_prase, a potential deadlock in
  ast_set_hangupsource & routing issues around outboundproxy.

