*asterisk-10.6.0 (11 Jul 2012)
*asterisk-1.8.14.0 (11 Jul 2012)

  11 Jul 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> asterisk-1.8.13.1.ebuild,
  +asterisk-1.8.14.0.ebuild, +asterisk-10.6.0.ebuild:
  Bugfix release on the 1.8 & 10 branches which drops chan_usbradio support.
  Amend SRC_URI as per Jaco Kroon in bug #425754. This fixes, among other
  things, a potential crash in mp3_read, a sip_pvt reference leak and
  overoptimisation for local channel chains. Adds voicemail storage backend
  selection support to 10.6.0, also by Jaco Kroon and first introduced for 1.8
  ebuilds. Distro patchset unchanged.

  09 Jul 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> -asterisk-1.8.12.1.ebuild:
  Remove old wrt bug 425050

