*asterisk-1.8.12.0 (03 May 2012)

  03 May 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -asterisk-1.8.10.1.ebuild,
  +asterisk-1.8.12.0.ebuild:
  Bugfix release; double FD closure patch by Jaco Kroon finally applied
  upstream. Also prevents chanspy from binding to zombie channels and removes
  an unnecessary ISDN hold restrictions on non-bridged calls. Removed
  vulnerable 1.8 branch ebuild now that a secure version is stable.

