*asterisk-10.0.0 (17 Dec 2011)

  17 Dec 2011; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +asterisk-10.0.0.ebuild:
  First release on the long-term support 10 branch. If you have not tried this
  on your production deployment yet, please set aside time now. This will be a
  stable candidate early in the new year. Patch by Jaco Kroon addresses bug
  #394459 by Agostino "ago" Sarubbo.

